#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cfeatures%5Cbusiness-rules-execution.md:40
msgid "Process execution flow Zorgtoeslag"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cfeatures%5Cbusiness-rules-execution.md:42
msgid ""
"sequenceDiagram\n"
"    participant F as Frontend\n"
"    participant B as Business API\n"
"    participant O as Operaton\n"
"    participant D as PostgreSQL\n"
"\n"
"    F->>B: POST /v1/process/zorgtoeslag/start\n"
"    B->>B: Validate JWT, extract claims\n"
"    B->>B: Map claims → process variables\n"
"    B->>O: POST /process-definition/key/zorgtoeslag/start\n"
"    O->>O: Execute BPMN workflow\n"
"    O->>O: Evaluate DMN decision table\n"
"    O->>B: Return process result\n"
"    B->>D: Write audit log entry\n"
"    B->>F: Return { eligible, amount }"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cfeatures%5Cbusiness-rules-execution.md:60
msgid ""
"**AWB Kapvergunning (tree felling permit)**\n"
"A two-layer BPMN process implementing the Dutch Administrative Law Act (Awb) "
"procedural requirements."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cfeatures%5Cbusiness-rules-execution.md:63
msgid ""
"The outer shell (`AwbShellProcess`) manages the six AWB phases: receipt "
"acknowledgement, completeness check, decision subprocess, and citizen "
"notification. It sets `receiptDate`, `awbDeadlineDate` (8 weeks per Awb 4:13)"
", and `dossierReference`."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cfeatures%5Cbusiness-rules-execution.md:65
msgid ""
"The inner subprocess (`TreeFellingPermitSubProcess`) handles the substantive "
"decision: it evaluates `TreeFellingDecision.dmn` and "
"`ReplacementTreeDecision.dmn`, creates a `Sub_CaseReview` user task for "
"caseworker review, and writes the final `permitDecision`, `status`, and "
"`finalMessage` variables back to the parent process."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cfeatures%5Cbusiness-rules-execution.md:67
msgid ""
"After the subprocess completes, the AWB shell creates a `Task_Phase6_Notify` "
"user task requiring the caseworker to confirm citizen notification before "
"the process ends."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cfeatures%5Cbusiness-rules-execution.md:71
msgid "Process execution flow Tree Felling permit"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cfeatures%5Cbusiness-rules-execution.md:72
msgid ""
"sequenceDiagram\n"
"    participant C as Citizen (Frontend)\n"
"    participant B as Business API\n"
"    participant O as Operaton\n"
"    participant CW as Caseworker (Frontend)\n"
"    participant D as PostgreSQL\n"
"\n"
"    C->>B: POST /v1/process/AwbShellProcess/start<br/>(treeDiameter, "
"protectedArea)\n"
"    B->>B: Validate JWT, inject tenant variables\n"
"    B->>O: POST /process-definition/key/AwbShellProcess/start\n"
"    O->>O: Phase 1 — set applicantId, productType, applicationDate\n"
"    O->>O: Phase 2 — set receiptDate, awbDeadlineDate, dossierReference\n"
"    O->>O: Phase 3 — evaluate AwbCompletenessCheck DMN\n"
"    O->>O: Call Activity → TreeFellingPermitSubProcess\n"
"    O->>O: Evaluate TreeFellingDecision DMN → permitDecision\n"
"    O->>O: Evaluate ReplacementTreeDecision DMN → replacementDecision\n"
"    O-->>O: Create user task: Sub_CaseReview\n"
"    B->>D: Write audit log entry\n"
"    B->>C: Return { processInstanceId, dossierReference }\n"
"\n"
"    Note over O: Process suspended — awaiting caseworker\n"
"\n"
"    CW->>B: GET /v1/task\n"
"    B->>O: GET /task?processVariables=municipality_eq_utrecht\n"
"    O->>B: Return task list\n"
"    B->>CW: Return open tasks\n"
"\n"
"    CW->>B: POST /v1/task/:id/claim\n"
"    B->>O: POST /task/:id/claim\n"
"    CW->>B: POST /v1/task/:id/complete<br/>(reviewAction, "
"reviewPermitDecision?)\n"
"    B->>O: POST /task/:id/complete\n"
"    O->>O: Set final status, decisionType, finalMessage\n"
"    O-->>O: Create user task: Task_Phase6_Notify\n"
"\n"
"    Note over O: Process suspended — awaiting notification confirmation\n"
"\n"
"    CW->>B: POST /v1/task/:id/complete<br/>(notificationMethod, "
"applicantNotified)\n"
"    B->>O: POST /task/:id/complete\n"
"    O->>O: Phase 6 complete — process ends\n"
"    B->>D: Write audit log entry"
msgstr ""

